# Site Configuration
# ===================

# For custom domain deployment (root level)
SITE=https://your-domain.com
PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=/

# For GitHub Pages subpath deployment, use:
# SITE=https://username.github.io/
# PUBLIC_BASE_PATH=/repository-name

# GitHub API Token (Optional)
# ============================
# Enables live repository data fetching with higher rate limits
# Create a token at: https://github.com/settings/tokens
# Required scopes: read-only public repository access
GITHUB_TOKEN=

# Anthropic API Key (Optional)
# ============================
# Enables automatic case study generation from GitHub repositories
# Get your key at: https://console.anthropic.com/
# Used during build to generate MDX files for new repositories
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Case Study Generation Options
# =============================
# REPO_SOURCE: Which repos to generate case studies for
#   - "pinned" = only pinned repos (requires GITHUB_TOKEN)
#   - "stars"  = only top starred repos
#   - "both"   = pinned first, then stars (default)
# REPO_SOURCE=both

# Custom Prompts (Optional)
# =========================
# Customize the AI prompts used for case study generation
# Run `npm run generate:copy-prompts` to create editable copies
#
# PROMPT_TEMPLATE = Path to main prompt template (default: scripts/prompts/case-study.md)
# SYSTEM_PROMPT   = Path to system prompt (default: scripts/prompts/system.md)
# CLAUDE_MODEL    = Model to use (default: claude-sonnet-4-20250514)
#
# Example:
# PROMPT_TEMPLATE=scripts/prompts-custom/case-study.md
# SYSTEM_PROMPT=scripts/prompts-custom/system.md
# CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
